ghly%20successful%20long-term%20value%20investor%2C%20with%20his%20Smead%20Value%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fsmead-value-fund-investor-class-us83178c8819%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESMVLX%3C%2Fa%3E)%20beating%2098%25%20of%20similar%20funds%20over%20the%20last%2015-year%20period%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar%20data.%20He%20has%20a%20knack%20for%20finding%20stocks%20that%20trade%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20and%20constantly%20warns%20investors%20about%20the%20dangers%20that%20passive%20indexes%20can%20pose%20at%20times%20when%20valuations%20are%20high%20and%20investors%20are%20excessively%20greedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20is%20one%20of%20those%20times%2C%20Smead%20thinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20my%20career%20(the%20first%20time%20for%20us%20at%20Smead%20Capital%20Management)%20that%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in%20the%20late%20stages%20of%20a%20major%20financial%20euphoria%20episode%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20note%2C%20he%20laid%20out%20a%20few%20arguments%20for%20why%20we're%20in%20a%20comparable%20spot%20to%20the%202000%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEquity%20ownership%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20household%20assets%20is%20at%20all-time%20highs.%20This%20may%20be%20partly%20due%20to%20investors%20chasing%20attractive%20returns%20in%20the%20market.%20But%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20signal%20that%20stock-market%20appreciation%20is%20simply%20outpacing%20gains%20in%20other%20asset%20classes%2C%20like%20real-estate%2C%20perhaps%20at%20an%20unsustainable%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22household%20equity%20ownership%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765e08763b028ed846a01d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESt.%20Louis%20Fed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20investors%20continue%20to%20bet%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20stocks%20in%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite%2C%20he%20said.%20Volatile%20stocks%20like%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia%20are%20up%2073%25%20and%20177%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20this%20year.%20Other%20speculative%20investments%20like%20bitcoin%20have%20been%20roaring%2C%20Smead%20pointed%20out.%20While%20it%20has%20dipped%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20is%20up%20119%25%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20sentiment%20can%20be%20a%20contrarian%20indicator%20of%20forward%20performance.%20Heightened%20interest%20in%20uber-risky%20assets%20can%20signal%20that%20investors%20are%20allowing%20greed%2C%20instead%20of%20fundamentals%2C%20to%20guide%20their%20decisions.%20Eventually%2C%20asset%20prices%20relative%20to%20earnings%20can%20simply%20become%20too%20expensive%20for%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20third%3A%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20most%20respected%20investors%20of%20the%20last%20forty%20years%20are%20sounding%20alarms%20that%20are%20falling%20on%20deaf%20ears.%26quot%3B%20Among%20those%20warning%20of%20expensive%20valuations%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-outlook-bubble-risks-kostin-einhorn-peltz-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGMO%20cofounder%20Jeremy%20Grantham%20and%20Research%20Affiliates%20founder%20Rob%20Arnott%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Smead%20published%20his%20note%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20back%2C%20the%20market%20has%20started%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20unraveling.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20went%20on%20a%2010-day%20losing%20streak%20and%20fell%20nearly%206%25.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20sank%20more%20than%203%25%20on%20Wednesday%20alone%20after%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20communicated%20its%20dissipating%20appetite%20for%20rate%20cuts%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20can't%20predict%20when%20a%20bubble%20will%20finally%20pop%2C%20Smead%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20market%20c