%20to%20receive%20security%20training.%20At%20Rush%20City%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20is%20just%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20reviewing%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20Vandevender's%20attack%20for%20his%20case%2C%20Tim%20Gravette%2C%20a%20corrections%20consultant%2C%20concluded%20that%20Rush%20City%20staffers%20were%20negligent%20for%20failing%20to%20properly%20follow%20state%20correction%20policies%2C%20and%20that%20if%20they%20had%2C%20Latimer%20couldn't%20have%20attacked%20Vandevender%20in%20the%20way%20he%20did.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20the%20lack%20of%20work%20material%20accountability%20to%20be%20unacceptable%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25263143-james-vandevender-v-walter-sass-gravette-letter%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Schnell%2C%20Minnesota's%20corrections%20commissioner%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20couldn't%20comment%20on%20Vandevender's%20case%20because%20it%20predated%20his%20tenure%2C%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20we%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20where%20we're%20trying%20to%20take%20the%20steps%20to%20keep%20people%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20since%20he%20became%20commissioner%20in%202019%2C%20he'd%20established%20an%20Office%20of%20Professional%20Accountability%20to%20address%20employee%20complaints%2C%20revived%20an%20independent%20ombudsman%20office%20to%20address%20internal%20grievances%2C%20started%20a%20body-camera%20pilot%20program%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Gomm's%20murder%2C%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20staff%20and%20cameras%20in%20the%20industry%20area%20of%20the%20prison%20where%20he%20died.%20The%20department%20confirmed%20that%20there%20have%20been%20no%20such%20changes%20at%20Rush%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20a%20prisoner%20wins%20or%20loses%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20Schnell%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20certainly%20looking%20at%20our%20practices