wnsize-retirement-mortgage-rates-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20risky%20corner%20of%20the%20ETF%20market%20has%20boomed%20this%20year%20as%20YOLO%20traders%20chase%20the%20rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221266%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nvidia%20stocks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616be6116bde8d4ead75b88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20fund%20that%20tracks%20Nvidia%20stock%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20leveraged%20ETFs.%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20risky%20corner%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20boomed%20in%202024%20amid%20another%20year%20of%20stellar%20gains.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraders%20have%20piled%20into%20leveraged%20single-stock%20ETFs%2C%20seeking%20to%20amplify%20returns%20on%20popular%20names%20like%20Nvidia.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20types%20of%20ETFs%20have%20attracted%20more%20than%20%2420%20billion%20in%20assets%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20stock%20market%20was%20an%20early%20frontier%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-odds-gambling-lines-memecoins-prediction-markets-polymarket-stocks-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20gambling%20craze%20that%20gripped%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20investors%20have%20driven%20a%20boom%20in%20a%20relatively%20new%20kind%20of%20investment%20product%20that%20can%20amplify%20gains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20losses%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20single%20name.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20leveraged%20single-stock%20exchange-traded%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20introduction%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20ETFs%20have%20been%20groundbreaking%20in%20offering%20the%20characteristics%20of%20a%20mutual%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20owning%20a%20basket%20of%20diversified%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20but%20offering%20the%20daily%20trading%20liquidity%20of%20a%20single%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20after%2030%20years%2C%20the%20humble%20ETF%20is%20seeing%20fresh%20updates%20that%20cater%20to%20investors%20with%20a%20strong%20appetite%20for%20risk.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20owning%20a%20basket%20of%20stocks%2C%20single-stock%20ETFs%20track%20the%20price%20of%20one%20stock%2C%20which%20the%20fund%20will%20try%20to%20juice%20returns%20on%20by%20levering%20up.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20vehicles%20that%20mass%20retail%20has%20never%20had%20the%20ability%20to%20trade%20before%2C%20until%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Todd%20Sohn%2C%20an%20ETF%20specialist%20at%20Strategas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fgraniteshares-2x-long-nvda-daily-etf-us38747r8271%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGraniteShares%202x%20Long%20NVDA%20Daily%20ETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeks%20to%20deliver%20double%20the%20move%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%3C%2Fa%3E%20daily%20price%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Nvidia%20stock%20jumped%20about%202.5%25%20amid%20a%20broader%20market%20rebound%2C%20while%20shares%20of%20the%202x%20Nvidia%20ETF%20returned%20nearly%205%25.%20Year-to-date%2C%20the%202x%20Nvidia%20ETF%20is%20up%20346%25%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20170%25%20gain%20for%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraders%20are%20looking%20to%20implement%20high-conviction%20ideas%20through%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Sohn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20these%20funds%2C%20making%20for%20some%20highly%20successful%20ETF%20launches%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%202x%20Nvidia%20ETF%20has%20attracted%20more%20than%20%245%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20while%20other%20popular%20leveraged%20ETFs%20tracking%20stocks%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmstr-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicroStrategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fcoin-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoinbase%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20each%20attracted%20well%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20the%20ETF%20space%2C%20where%20the%20breakeven%20point%20for%20most%20ETF%20products%20is%20around%20%2450%20million%20in%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20white-label%20ETF%20provider%20Alpha%20Architect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-to-date%2C%20more%20than%2060%20ETFs%20have%20launched%20catering%20to%20single-stocks%2C%20attracting%20a%20combined%20%2423%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20Sohn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20amounts%20to%20relative%20peanuts%20in%20the%20%2410%20trillion%20universe%20of%20ETFs%2C%20it's%20still%20notable%2C%20and%20the%20funds%20are%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20use.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20pop%20up%20quite%20often%20on%20the%20most%20traded%20ETFs%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20Sohn%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20ETFs%20linked%20to%20Nvidia%2C%20Tesla%2C%20Coinbase%2C%20and%20MicroStrategy%20are%20the%20most%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20they%20can%20deliver%20outsize%20returns%2C%20these%20investment%20vehicles%20are%20inherently%20risky%2C%20much%20more%20so%20than%20owning%20the%20underlying%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESohn%20said%20that%20leveraged%20ETFs%20are%20incredibly%20volatile%2C%20and%20due%20to%20options%20decay%2C%20they're%20best%20used%20as%20a%20trading%20vehicle%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20set%20it%20and%20forget%20it%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20Sohn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptions%20decay%20refers%20to%20the%20idea%20that%2C%20even%20if%20the%20underlying%20stock%20trades%20sideways%2C%20the%20leveraged%20ETFs%20would%20likely%20move%20lower%20as%20options%20expire%20with%20zero%20value%20and%20new%20contracts%20are%20purchased.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20leveraged%20downside%20tied%20to%20these%20ETFs%20can%20be%20painful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Nvidia's%20summer%20correction%2C%20the%202x%20long%20Nvidia%20ETF%20lost%20about%2063%25%2C%20prompting%20concern%20from%20Redditors%20who%20invested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20I've%20lost%20a%20ton%20on%20NVDL%20(not%20touching%20my%20NVDA)%20and%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20think%20what%20makes%20the%20most%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FNVDA_Stock%2Fcomments%2F1dng4i2%2Fconfession_i_invested_in_nvdl_at_what_looks_to%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERedditor%20said%20in%20a%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Nvidia%20subreddit%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20is%20MicroStrategy%20stock%2C%20which%20is%20down%20about%2033%25%20from%20its%20late%20November%20peak%2C%20while%20the%202x%20ETF%20that%20tracks%20the%20stock%20is%20down%20more%20than%2060%25%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trading%20craze%20recalls%20another%20popular%20recent%20high-risk%20investment%20trend%E2%80%94%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwhat-are-zero-day-expiration-options-stock-market-risks-0dte-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20zero-day%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20contracts%20are%20a%20bet%20on%20the%20single-day%20move%20in%20a%20stock%2C%20with%20the%20option%20expiring%20the%20same%20day%20a%20trader%20buys%20it.%20The%20market%20took%20off%20during%20the%20pandemic%20trading%20boom%2C%20and%20it%20got%20so%20big%20that%20JPMorgan%20warned%20last%20year%20that%20its%20popularity%20could%20spark%20bouts%20of%20volatility%20in%20the%20broader%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20now%2C%20the%20risks%20appear%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20individual%20traders%20who%20are%20buying%20them%20and%20not%20the%20broader%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20single-stock%20leveraged%20ETFs%20have%20gained%20in%20popularity%20this%20year%2C%20they%20remain%20relatively%20small%20in%20size.%20For%20example%2C%20NVDL%20has%20%245.5%20billion%20in%20assets%20and%20NVIDIA%20is%20a%20%243%20trillion%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20Todd%20Rosenbluth%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20TMX%20VettaFi%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20risk-on%20traders%20seem%20less%20concerned%20about%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20single-stock%20ETFs%20and%20more%20focused%20on%20which%20one%20will%20take%20off%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20questions%20is%E2%80%A6%20what%20name%20catches%20on%20next%20with%20the%20trading%20crowd%3F%20Palantir%20seems%20to%20be%20one%20candidate%20(and%20has%202x%20ETFs%20out%20there).%20But%20we'll%20see%20what%20else%20comes%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Sohn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleveraged-etf-single-stock-etfs-nvidia-microstrategy-nvdl-traders-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734771602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765ce625cddac6581d76078%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fleveraged-etf-single-stock-etfs-nvidia-microstrategy-nvdl-traders-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%2060%20leveraged%20single-stock%20ETFs%20have%20launched%20this%20year%2C%20attracting%20more%20than%20%2420%20billion%20in%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A90%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fleveraged-etf-single-stock-etfs-nvidia-microstrategy-nvdl-traders-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7