20would%20come%20at%20a%20cost%20to%20our%20partners%20by%20regulating%20how%20they%20must%20go%20about%20picking%20the%20best%20search%20engine%20for%20their%20customers.%20And%20they%20would%20impose%20burdensome%20restrictions%20and%20oversight%20over%20contracts%20that%20have%20reduced%20prices%20for%20devices%20and%20supported%20innovation%20in%20rival%20browsers%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20been%20good%20for%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20a%20group%20of%20states%20asked%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20to%20force%20Google%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-officials-urge-judge-order-google-sell-chrome-search-antitrust-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esell%20its%20Chrome%20browser%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20resolve%20the%20case.%20They%20also%20asked%20that%20Google%20be%20stopped%20from%20entering%20default%20search%20agreements%20with%20Apple%20and%20other%20companies%20and%20that%20Google%20should%20open%20its%20search%20engine%20results%20to%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sell-chrome-search-winners-losers-doj-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20Chrome%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20would%20open%20up%20the%20browser%20market%20and%20would%20likely%20be%20cheered%20on%20by%20search%20rivals%20and%20advertisers%2C%20though%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20a%20possible%20Chrome%20spinoff%20might%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20will%20present%20arguments%20for%20their%20proposals%20at%20a%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20April.%20The%20judge%20is%20expected%20to%20rule%20on%20the%20final%20remedies%20by%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKent%20Walker%2C%20Google's%20president%20of%20global%20affairs%2C%20previously%20said%20the%20company%20intends%20to%20appeal%20the%20judge's%20ruling%2C%20potentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-doj-battle-best-worst-scenarios-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelaying%20a%20final%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20antitrust%20division%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-proposal-remedies-resolve-search-antitrust-case-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734752496000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676595971cee543535a88099%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-proposal-remedies-resolve-search-antitrust-case-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20made%20its%20own%20proposals%20to%20remedy%20antitrust%20violations%20after%20the%20Justice%20Department%20proposed%20Google%20sell%20its%20Chrome%20browser.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40insider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-proposal-remedies-resolve-search-antitrust-case-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Trump-Musk%20friendship%20doomed%20to%20fail%3F%20Seth%20Meyers%20predicts%20a%20'disastrous'%20future%20for%20the%20alliance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734752389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116523619%2Cimgsize-908458.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-trump-musk-friendship-doomed-to-fail-seth-meyers-predicts-a-disastrous-future-for-the-alliance%2Farticleshow%2F116521893.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime