20provided%20a%20grant%20that%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20set%20up%20facilities%20for%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%20groundnuts.%20This%20primary%20processing%20would%20enable%20farmers%20to%20retain%20a%20higher%20portion%20of%20the%20profits.%20By%20working%20collectively%2C%20the%20farmers%20could%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20produce%20and%20access%20better%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20fresh%20produce%20delivery%20service%20in%202020%20evolved%20into%20Nutty%20Village%20in%202022.%20With%20a%20vision%20to%20empower%20farmers%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20aims%20to%20help%20them%20establish%20their%20own%20processing%20units%2C%20directly%20sourcing%20high-quality%20produce%20at%20fair%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20champion%20both%20the%20exceptional%20products%20these%20farmers%20create%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270093%2Fpeanut-jaggery-health-benefits-indian-food-recipe-for-chikki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20proteins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20through%20our%20peanut%20butters%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUplifting%20rural%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20their%20primary%20processing%20units%2C%20Aman%20started%20purchasing%20the%20processed%20groundnuts%20at%20Rs%20100-120%20per%20kilogram%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20prices%20they%20were%20getting.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20primary%20processing%20is%20now%20done%20by%20these%20farmers%2C%20they%20also%20have%20their%20own%20seeds%20to%20put%20back%20into%20harvesting%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20Aman%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20could%20all%20work%20together%20for