ges%20such%20as%20courier%20transportation%20glitches%20and%20packaging%20issues.%20They%20pack%20their%20candles%20in%20Longpi%20jars%20using%20eco-friendly%20materials%20like%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20boxes.%20Large%20Longpi%20jar%20candles%2C%20containing%20approximately%201%20kg%20of%20soy%20wax%2C%20are%20priced%20at%20around%20Rs%203%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOctober%20Pumpkin%20has%20also%20participated%20in%20two%20pop-up%20stalls%20at%20Nagaland%20House%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20under%20%E2%80%98Home%20%26amp%3B%20Heart%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20collective%20of%20Northeast%20women%20entrepreneurs%20based%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Zero-energy%20low-cost%20cold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20West%20Khasi%20Hills%20struggle%20with%20warehousing%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20logistics.%20The%20lack%20of%20affordable%2C%20energy-efficient%20storage%20solutions%20for%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20often%20results%20in%20significant%20post-harvest%20losses%20and%20reduced%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20small%20project%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20the%20non-profit%20driving%20this%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%20So%20far%2C%20three%20units%20have%20been%20constructed%20in%20different%20villages%2C%20each%20costing%20Rs%201.64%20lakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NSSS%20works%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20community%20in%20several%20areas%20like%20farming%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20child%20services.%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20projects%20for%20farmers.%20I%20mobilise%20farmers%20and%20also%20help%20them%20access%20assistance%20from%20government%20and%20private%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20these%20storage%20units%20came%20from%20the%20farmers%20themselves.%20Struggling%20to%20store%20their%20produce%2C%20they%20faced%20losses%20even%20before%20reaching%20the%20markets%2C%20compounded%20by%20low%20prices.%20While%20the%20project%20began%20in%202019%2C%20its%20progress%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSSS%20oversees%20the%20construction%20of%20these%20units%20by%20hiring%20contractors%2C%20using%20locally%20available%20materials%20like%20burned%20bricks%2C%20river%20sand%2C%20bamboo%20poles%2C%20CGI%20sheets%2C%20iron%20nails%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20pebbles.%20Each%20unit%20can%20store%20up%20to%20a%20tonne%20of%20produce%2C%20preserving%20it%20for%20one%20to%20four%20weeks.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20units%20are%20quick%20to%20construct%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20just%20a%20day%20or%20two%20%E2%80%94%20and%20require%20no%20maintenance.%20Farmers%20can%20use%20them%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20fill%20the%20gap%20between%20two%20layers%20of%20the%20structure%20with%20river%20sand%20and%20pebbles.%20This%20sand%20is%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%20This%20keeps%20the%20produce%20cool.%20Each%20unit%20benefits%20over%20120%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388012%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBinolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cold%20storage%20units%2C%20though%20rooted%20in%20scientific%20principles%2C%20involve%20no%20elaborate%20technology.%20They%20are%20managed%20by%20the%20Village%20Executive%20Committee%20(VEC)%2C%20ensuring%20equitable%20access%20for%20all%20villagers%20while%20keeping%20produce%20clean%20and%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20Meghalaya%20Basin%20Management%20Agency%20(MBMA)%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20handling%20externally%20aided%20government%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20under%20an%20innovation%20fund%20that%20helps%20improve%20or%20scale%20up%20solutions.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Community-Led%20Landscape%20Management%20Project%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20addressing%20natural%20resource%20management%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wankit%20Swer%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20MBMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20farmers%20are%20smallholders%20with%20limited%20production.%20After%20meeting%20their%20own%20needs%2C%20the%20excess%20is%20sold.%20Without%20proper%20storage%2C%20they%20often%20resort%20to%20distress%20sales%20of%20perishable%20items.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314446%2Fchennai-student-eco-friendly-tech-increases-produce-shelf-life-sunharvested-coolrooms%2F%5C%22%3Ecold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20prevent%20such%20sales%20and%20provide%20a%20better%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Anti-microbial%20fabric%20made%20from%20banana%20fibre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland-based%20venture%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%20is%20making%20remarkable%20progress%20in%20harnessing%20banana%20fibre.%20%E2%80%9COur%20banana%20fibre%20project%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Runway%20India%E2%80%99%20division%20of%20our%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20venture.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD)%20phase%2C%20working%20on%20producing%20fabric%20from%20banana%20fibre%2C%20which%20boasts%20anti-microbial%20properties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-microbial%20properties%20of%20banana%20fibre%2C%20derived%20from%20natural%20compounds%20in%20the%20plant%2C%20create%20a%20protective%20shield%20on%20the%20fabric%2C%20inhibiting%20the%20growth%20of%20bacteria%20and%20fungi.%20This%20fabric%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20used%20in%20medical%20textiles%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20integrate%20additional%20functional%20properties%2C%20such%20as%20water%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20-%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20%E2%80%93%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354933%2Fombak-sustainable-furniture-shruthi-prakash-rattan-chairs-table-wall-decor-from-banana-fibres-in-indonesia-india%2F%5C%22%3EBanana%20fibre%20is%20also%20an%20eco-friendly%20alternative%20to%20polymer-based%20fabrics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20biodegradable.%20Moreover%2C%20banana%20pl