y.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coarser%20type%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20coasters%20while%20the%20delicate%20variety%20can%20be%20used%20to%20craft%20jewellery%20and%20hair%20extensions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20banana%20fibre%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banana%20%E2%80%98pseudostem%E2%80%99%20is%20passed%20through%20rollers%20(like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20sugarcane)%20and%20the%20mulch%20is%20extracted.%20What%20remains%20is%20the%20fibre%2C%20which%20is%20washed%2C%20dried%2C%20segregated%2C%20combed%20(to%20get%20various%20grades)%20and%20graded%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20products%20made%20and%20sold%20by%20the%20company%20using%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20are%20vases%2C%20planters%2C%20jewellery%2C%20bags%2C%20clutches%2C%20coasters%2C%20table%20mats%2C%20wall%20hangings%2C%20lanterns%20and%20baskets.%20The%20prices%20of%20these%20products%20range%20from%20Rs%20300%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20says%20Nengneithem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Products%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EProducts%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20two%20units%20in%20Dimapur%20and%20Athibung%2C%20employing%20over%2030%20artisans.%20We%20provide%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20as%20eco-friendly%20fillers%20for%20packaging.%20We%20also%20use%20these%20materials%20to%20package%20our%20own%20handicrafts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20product%20is%20delivered%2C%20customers%20can%20repurpose%20the%20fibre%20from%20the%20packaging%20in%20their%20gardens%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20valuable%20nutrients%20for%20plants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunway%20India%20has%20also%20explored%20creating%20paper%20from%20banana%20stem%20mulch.%20This%20paper%20is%20used%20for%20wrapping%20handicrafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20crafting%20greeting%20cards%20and%20flower%20bouquets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fo1Jdi9AQA4A%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraining%20and%20capacity%20building%20are%20central%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20The%20enterprise%20has%20partnered%20with%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20women%20in%20areas%20affected%20by%20poverty%20and%20insurgency.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20conducts%20workshops%20in%20schools%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(2020)%20skill%20development%20module.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Light%2C%20sturdy%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountry%20boats%20are%20prone%20to%20leaks%20and%20instability%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20fatal%20accidents%20each%20year.%20While%20fibre-glass%20boats%20are%20a%20common%20alternative%2C%20they%20are%20neither%20biodegradable%20nor%20recyclable%2C%20often%20ending%20up%20in%20rivers%20and%20causing%20significant%20environmental%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20founded%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20in%20Assam%20in%202020.%20His%20startup%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20inland%20water%20transport%20by%20creating%20safer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337729%2Fbihar-bamboo-startup-entrepreneur-satyam-sundaram-eco-friendly-products-profits%2F%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20composite%20boats%2C%20offering%20sustainable%20water%20mobility%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20innovation%20took%20over%20two%20years%20to%20materialise.%20Our%20boats%20are%20made%20of%2085%20percent%20bamboo%2C%2010%20percent%20polymers%2C%20and%20five%20percent%20fibre-glass.%20The%20main%20advantage%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20is%20their%20sustainability.%20Bamboo%20is%20six%20times%20more%20sustainable%20than%20hardwood%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fast-growing%2C%20abundant%2C%20and%20incredibly%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22w